# Target Companies / Organizations — EXAMPLE
# Copy this file to config/target_companies.md and replace with your list.
# Also copy to rag_sources/target_companies.md (used in RAG context for REPL mode).
#
# The pipeline is field-agnostic. Replace the placeholders below with employers
# relevant to YOUR field — companies, nonprofits, school districts, government
# agencies, hospital systems, consulting firms, etc.

## Tier 1 — Active Focus
# Employers you'd take a role at today if the right position opened up.
# The scorer applies a "Tier 1 bonus" — in-domain roles at these get scored at least 6.
- [Employer One]
